snippet.title: Deadly Heart Gambit (Gameplay Trailer)
snippet.description:
You only have 3 months left to live. Gamble for extra time in Alice-sama’s life-or-death game. 
Be careful — she wants to steal your heart. 🔪💜

Wishlist "Deadly Heart Gambit" on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3202110/

This is my second game on Steam! 🥰
Please subscribe to this channel, thank you! ^^
